{"data":[{"date":"19:46 01/07","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs HAGL tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 17 V-League 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/ket-qua-quang-nam-vs-hagl.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs HAGL tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 17 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai v\u00f2ng 17 V-League 2018 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 1/7.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs HAGL: 2-2<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n: V\u0103n To\u00e0n (45'+1; 55'); Thanh Trung (73'); Minh Tu\u1ea5n (76')</p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHAGL b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Qu\u1ea3ng Nam tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 v\u1edbi tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u00e2m l\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n sau chu\u1ed7i 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eebng \u2018ca kh\u00fac kh\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n\u2019 sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 3-2 t\u1ea1i c\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap h\u1ecd t\u1ef1 tin tr\u00e0n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c. Ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HAGL c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 sang t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Thanh T\u00f9ng t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t khung th\u00e0nh CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam trong gang t\u1ea5c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs HAGL v\u00f2ng 17 V-League 2018 chi\u1ec1u h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs HAGL v\u00f2ng 17 V-League 2018 chi\u1ec1u h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Ket-qua-Quang-Nam-vs-HAGL-vong-17-V-League-2018-chieu-hom-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs HAGL chia \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf v\u00f2ng 17 V-League</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. Qu\u1ea3ng Nam ch\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3 y\u1ebfu \u1edbt v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng V\u0103n To\u00e0n ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd hi\u1ec7p 1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, HAGL c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 55. Sau khi \u0111o\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t nhanh t\u1eeb trung v\u1ec7 Thiago, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh V\u0103n C\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0 cho HAGL.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch an to\u00e0n tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y t\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn b\u1edfi t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 73 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi sau qu\u1ea3 penalty m\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i cho r\u1eb1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m tay trung v\u1ec7 Zeba c\u1ee7a HAGL trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. Tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, Thanh Trung d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, r\u00fat ng\u1eafn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 xu\u1ed1ng 1-2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2. Sau khi b\u00f3ng d\u1ed9i x\u00e0 b\u1eadt ra tr\u00fang ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o H\u00e0 Minh Tu\u1ea5n b\u0103ng v\u00e0o d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 cho CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">2-2 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0 HAGL ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i ra v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau v\u00f2ng 17.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3926","checkdouble":"190089"},{"date":"19:55 01/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 2-2 HAGL: C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/van-toan-ghi-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u1edf v\u00f2ng 17 V-League.</h2><h2>1. C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi ghi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. V\u00e0 t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi ghi th\u00eam hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng pha ghi b\u00e0n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc song n\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat HAGL. N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng V\u0103n To\u00e0n chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 s\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Van Toan ghi cu dup ban thang cho HAGL\" title=\"V\u0103n To\u00e0n ghi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/van-toan-ghi-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>&nbsp;</em><i>\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 2-2 HAGL l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c V\u0103n To\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh HAGL<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong l\u1ea7n ra m\u1eaft CLB HAGL, trung v\u1ec7 Josip Zeba \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. Anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn t\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a HAGL.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn, Josip Zeba \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn HAGL b\u1ecb th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t 11m. \u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y ngo\u1ea1i binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m n\u00e1ch, tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 tay v\u00e0o ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t 11m. V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y, \u0110inh Thanh Trung \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n r\u00fat ng\u1eafn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 xu\u1ed1ng 1-2 cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ngo\u1ea1i binh Josip Zeba v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i \u1edf HAGL sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. Th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a HAGL<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong hi\u1ec7p 1 tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00e1i n\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Tam K\u1ef3, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. H\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 3 ph\u00fat. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. R\u1ea5t may \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam ghi th\u00eam v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn, khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a cho hai \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u1eabn l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nan gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi HAGL. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>4. Qu\u1ea3ng Nam g\u1eb7p may<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1eddi r\u1ea1c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c trong hi\u1ec7p 1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 2 b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1i ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong m\u1ed9t n\u00e0y m\u00e0 may m\u1eafn song h\u00e0nh, nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha th\u1ed5i penalty c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam gi\u1ea3m t\u1ea3i s\u1ee9c \u00e9p, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i ch\u1ec9 2 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 may m\u1eafn c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Minh Tu\u1ea5n. T\u1eeb c\u00fa s\u00fat xa c\u1ee7a Huy H\u00f9ng, b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m x\u00e0 khung th\u00e0nh HAGL r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1eadp l\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Minh Tu\u1ea5n c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Qu\u1ea3ng Nam may m\u1eafn gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t HAGL \u0111ang h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf sau hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>5. Th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League 2018 sau vong 17\" title=\"BXH V-League 2018 sau v\u00f2ng 17\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/BXH-V-League-sau-vong-17.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HAGL v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 5 tr\u00ean BXH V-League 2018 sau v\u00f2ng 17</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 5 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 24 \u0111i\u1ec3m. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u1edbi t\u1ed1p 2 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau khi Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam c\u0169ng b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1ed1p \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi 22 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 17 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u. L\u00fac n\u00e0y h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 8. Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp sau v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 1 v\u00e0 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9, vi\u1ec7c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 b\u1ecb t\u1ee5t h\u1ea1ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/quang-nam-vs-hagl-vleague-2018-372-190082.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/ket-qua-quang-nam-vs-hagl.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/quang-nam-vs-hagl-vleague-2018-372-190082.html\">Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 2-2 HAGL (KT): D\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i Tam K\u1ef3</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs HAGL: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai v\u00f2ng 17 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tien-dao-rimario-da-co-ben-do-moi-sau-khi-chia-tay-hagl-168-190063.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/tien-dao-rimario-da-co-ben-do-moi-sau-khi-chia-tay-hagl.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tien-dao-rimario-da-co-ben-do-moi-sau-khi-chia-tay-hagl-168-190063.html\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Rimario \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi sau khi chia tay HAGL?</span><br>\r\nSau khi b\u1ecb CLB HAGL thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Rimario \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp theo t\u1ea1i V-League. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-chieu-mo-dong-huong-voi-luka-modric-de-va-hang-thu-168-189946.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/hagl-chieu-mo-dong-huong-voi-luka-modric-de-va-hang-thu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-chieu-mo-dong-huong-voi-luka-modric-de-va-hang-thu-168-189946.html\">HAGL th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Luka Modric cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai HAGL \u0111ang th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c ngo\u1ea1i binh th\u1ee9 hai cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a V-League 2018 mang t\u00ean Josip Zeba t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Croatia.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3925","checkdouble":"190109"},{"date":"05:20 02/07","title":"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Th\u00e1i Lan?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-dang-tiec-truoc-u19-thai-lan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, HLV U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u00f4ng Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i.</h2><h2>HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 k\u1ef5 d\u01a1 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 \u0111em sang Indonesia \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t hay kh\u00f4ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Th\u00e1i Lan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Th\u00e1i Lan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/dsc00001-0142.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc: \u201cH\u00f4m nay ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u00e1i Lan l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i. Nh\u01b0ng x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u01a1n l\u00e0 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc v\u00e0 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam: \u201cV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u01b0a th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1ecbu tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u1eafng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. Nh\u1eefng sai s\u1ed1 trong d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U19 Phlippines. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 15h30, ng\u00e0y 03/07.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-thai-lan-325-190103.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/ban-thang-u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-thai-lan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-thai-lan-325-190103.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 0-0 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan (Gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)</span><br>\r\nNgay l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn U19 Th\u00e1i Lan. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-thai-lan-15h30-ngay-17-372-190078.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-thai-lan-15h30-ngay-17.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-thai-lan-15h30-ngay-17-372-190078.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 0-0 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan (KT): Phung ph\u00ed c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3924","checkdouble":"190139"},{"date":"05:52 02/07","title":"\u0110\u1ec3 thua t\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, HLV Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/2/de-thua-tuong-moi-cua-sai-gon-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ec3 thua S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 l\u1ea1i tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ec3 thua S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 l\u1ea1i tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/HLV-VAN-SY2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 t\u1ed1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb &nbsp;\u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 17 V-League b\u1eb1ng chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i BXH.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1edfi c\u01a1n m\u01b0a n\u1eb7ng h\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00e1 &lsquo;nh\u1ea1t&rsquo;. Ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi gi\u00fap cho S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 tranh ch\u1ea5p, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eaft c\u00f2i nh\u01b0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t d\u1eabn t\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 h\u01a1i \u00e1c&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, d\u00f9 t\u00e2n HLV c\u1ee7a CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng&nbsp;kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi h\u1ecdp b\u00e1i nh\u01b0ng tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng l\u00e0 HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n Phong c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m vui sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Vi\u1ec7c CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n thay HLV ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn cho t\u00e2m l\u00ed anh em c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. Nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch c\u1edfi b\u1ecf t\u00e2m l\u00ed, ch\u01a1i \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, n\u00f3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng, v\u00e0 h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng l\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3923","checkdouble":"190140"},{"date":"19:19 01/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 1/7: Kroos b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/23/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-17-kroos-bao-tin-buon-cho-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 1/7.</h2><h2>Juventus nh\u1eafm si\u00eau sao Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Tuttosport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Cristiano Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd t\u1edbi ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Juventus h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Bernabeu khi kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 31.5 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb Real. C\u1ea3 PSG v\u00e0 Man United c\u0169ng \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u00e3 5 l\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Martial</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Daily Star kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bayern Munich l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Anthony Martial. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Franck Ribery v\u00e0 Arjen Robben \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00ean kia s\u01b0\u1eddn d\u1ed1c s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. V\u00e0 Martial \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean l\u00e0m m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Bavaria.</div>\r\n<h2>Kroos t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 17 Kroos b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 17 Kroos b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/11/Diem-tin-Bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-17-Kroos-bao-tin-buon-cho-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 1/7:\u00a0Kroos t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Man United</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Mundo Deportivo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toni Kroos s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Real \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Man United h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho. Nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Kroos mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Bernabeu t\u1edbi h\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2022. Kroos tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola t\u1ea1i Man City.</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea t\u00ednh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Liverpool v\u1ee5 Alisson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Daily Mail \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma. The Blues nh\u1eafm Alisson nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Courtois, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp s\u1eeda chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Uruguay</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng theo t\u1edd Daily Mail, Arsenal \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/neville-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-arsenal-sau-tran-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-469-190073.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lucas Torreira</span>. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u0169ng \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n s\u00e2n Emirates. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, Arsenal ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y sau khi World Cup kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. Uruguay s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 6/7 t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>Karius v\u1eabn l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd The Sun, Loris Karius d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Liverpool sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea3ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00fat lui kh\u1ecfi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, l\u00fd do l\u00e0 ph\u00eda Roma \u0111\u00f2i m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft. Vi\u1ec7c Jack Butland l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Stoke khi\u1ebfn Liverpool kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u00f4ng c\u1eady v\u00e0o Karius \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-306-tro-cung-mourinho-bat-ngo-o-lai-mu-184-189977.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 30/6: Tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Mourinho b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-296-mu-muon-chieu-mo-sao-tuyen-duc-chelsea-sap-co-bom-tan-184-189959.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 29/6: M.U mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3922","checkdouble":"190106"},{"date":"21:35 01/07","title":"R\u1eddi World Cup 2018, Ronaldo s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/1/roi-world-cup-2018-ronaldo-sap-co-ben-do-moi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italia, Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</h2><h2>Ronaldo chia tay Real sau World Cup?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"R\u1eddi World Cup 2018, Ronaldo chia tay Real \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"R\u1eddi World Cup 2018, Ronaldo chia tay Real \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Roi-World-Cup-2018,-Ronaldo-chia-tay-Real-de-toi-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ronaldo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo sau khi anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1/8 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ed1i qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ngo\u00e0i m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i du l\u1ecbch ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng th\u00ec ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn CR7 c\u0169ng \u0111ang ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 kh\u1edfi tranh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p \u0111\u00f2i t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real l\u00e0 350.000 b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u00edt so v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c 619.000 b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Neymar. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do \u0111\u00f3 si\u00eau sao 33 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 1,35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n.V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu y\u00eau c\u1ea7u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ronaldo chia tay Real c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n hi\u1ec7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd b\u00e1o ti\u1ebfng \u00dd Tuttosport \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00ec Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB Juventus trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi m\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y CLB Real Madrid gi\u1ea3m ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha xu\u1ed1ng 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (kho\u1ea3ng 130 tri\u1ec7u USD). Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Real t\u1eebng treo gi\u00e1 884 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\u00a0cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ronaldo.\u00a0<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tan-man/bong-da-tro-choi-cua-tap-the-392-190025.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/bong-da-tro-choi-cua-tap-the.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tan-man/bong-da-tro-choi-cua-tap-the-392-190025.html\">Messi - Ronaldo: B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 - tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp th\u1ec3</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00eam nay, m\u1ecdi con m\u1eaft ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o hai si\u00eau sao n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd b\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u hay ho kh\u00e1c....</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thua-uruguay-hlv-bo-dao-nha-xin-ronaldo-mot-dieu-421-190047.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/santos.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thua-uruguay-hlv-bo-dao-nha-xin-ronaldo-mot-dieu-421-190047.html\">Thua Uruguay, HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha xin Ronaldo m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u</span><br>\r\nFernando Santos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 63 tu\u1ed5i hy v\u1ecdng Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho Seleccao thay v\u00ec chia tay \u0110TQG.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhm-rat-buon-khi-khong-co-messi-va-ronaldo-o-tu-ket-421-190050.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/nhm-rat-buon-khi-khong-co-messi-va-ronaldo-o-tu-ket.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhm-rat-buon-khi-khong-co-messi-va-ronaldo-o-tu-ket-421-190050.html\">NHM r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</span><br>\r\nGary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi, c\u1ef1u sao MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh NHM s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3921","checkdouble":"190117"},{"date":"18:02 01/07","title":"\u0110\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u1ea1nh tranh sao s\u00e1ng World Cup c\u00f9ng Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/tottenham-muon-mua-quintero-cung-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Quintero, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Colombia \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Quintero g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf Porto, Juan Quintero \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho River Plate c\u1ee7a Argentina m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong v\u00f2ng 1 n\u0103m. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00f9i trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Colombia v\u00e0 Nam M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i River, s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Quintero \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed3i sinh. Anh d\u1ea7n t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u0169ng nh\u1eefng pha \u0111i b\u00f3ng l\u1eaft l\u00e9o. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0110T Colombia tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Quintero, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Colombia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Quintero, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Colombia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/tottenham-muon-mua-quintero-cung-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Quintero, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Colombia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, Quintero \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Ba Lan hay Senegal \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh t\u1ea1i Medellin, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 l\u1edbn th\u1ee9 2 Colombia \u0111\u1ec1u tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, anh c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Real v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Quintero t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i. Sau Real Madrid, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Quintero. \u0110\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00eam s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho Harry Kane, Spurs mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Porto.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Quintero kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Tottenham hay Real. L\u00fd do l\u00e0 b\u1edfi River c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n mua \u0111\u1ee9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 5 tri\u1ec7u Euro theo nh\u01b0 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 Argentina kh\u00f3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Quintero l\u00e2u d\u00e0i, song h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n ki\u1ebfm l\u1eddi t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ee9c h\u00fat c\u1ee7a Quintero, nghe \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o River s\u1ebd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t anh r\u1ed3i b\u00e1n l\u1ea1i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i World Cup, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Anh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8, con s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n c\u00f2n t\u0103ng l\u00ean cao h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-muon-vuot-mat-mu-va-tottenham-vu-ronaldo-han-quoc-172-189950.html\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU v\u00e0 Tottenham v\u1ee5 Ronaldo H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-va-tottenham-dai-chien-vi-tien-dao-la-172-189945.html\">Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u1ea1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lo-ben-do-moi-cua-mateo-kovacic-180-189349.html\">L\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Mateo Kovacic</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/bayern-munich-va-tottenham-dai-chien-vi-sao-real-madrid-180-189278.html\">Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3920","checkdouble":"190101"},{"date":"22:11 01/07","title":"N\u00d3NG: Arsenal s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/24/nong-arsenal-sap-co-tan-binh-thu-3.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf S\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9, CLB Arsenal \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 ba mang t\u00ean Sokratis Papastathopoulos sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Anh.</h2><h2>Arsenal s\u1eafp c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a\u00a0<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sokratis Papastathopoulos\u00a0</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc nhi\u1ec1u sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, CLB Arsenal \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis Papastathopoulos t\u1eeb CLB Borussia Dortmund.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u00f3ng Arsenal s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh Sokratis Papastathopoulos h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u00f3ng Arsenal s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh Sokratis Papastathopoulos h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/3/11/Nong-Arsenal-sap-co-tan-binh-Sokratis-Papastathopoulos-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Arsenal \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u00e0n v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mang t\u00ean Sokratis Papastathopoulos</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Ruhr v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2013, khi \u1ea5y c\u00f2n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp, Sokratis \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay, anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh 192 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Dortmund v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Bundesliga. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn bao g\u1ed3m Arsenal v\u00e0 c\u00e1c CLB t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Manchester United, Juventus hay Chelsea.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc phong \u0111\u1ed9 ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Dortmund, Papastathopoulos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o v\u00e0ng-\u0111en \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n tham v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u. V\u00e0 Arsenal c\u0169ng n\u1eafm b\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady c\u1ea3 2 b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. N\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 ba Arsenal mua sao Dortmund, sau c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Sven Mislintat v\u00e0 Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh, Sokratis \u0111\u00e3 bay \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn London t\u1eeb\u00a0 Kalamata, Hy L\u1ea1p v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y l\u00fac 7h t\u1ed1i (gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng). Anh ta c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi v\u1ee3 v\u00e0 cha m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 Ba c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh Stephan Lichtsteiner v\u00e0 Bernd Leno.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chot-thoi-diem-arsenal-cong-bo-tan-binh-25-trieu-bang-172-190091.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/chot-thoi-diem-arsenal-cong-bo-tan-binh-25-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chot-thoi-diem-arsenal-cong-bo-tan-binh-25-trieu-bang-172-190091.html\">Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Arsenal c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nArsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Torreira t\u1eeb Sampdoria, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/neville-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-arsenal-sau-tran-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-469-190073.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/neville-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-arsenal-sau-tran-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/neville-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-arsenal-sau-tran-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-469-190073.html\">Neville khen ng\u1ee3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span><br>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal, Lucas Torreira sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Uruguay v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00eam qua.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-va-chelsea-theo-duoi-ngoi-sao-dt-colombia-172-189966.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/arsenal-va-chelsea-theo-duoi-ngoi-sao-dt-colombia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-va-chelsea-theo-duoi-ngoi-sao-dt-colombia-172-189966.html\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao \u0110T Colombia</span><br>\r\nThi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 James Rodriguez \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh l\u00e0 Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3919","checkdouble":"190121"},{"date":"15:09 01/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh Politano n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi gia nh\u1eadp Inter?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/1/politano-phat-bieu-ve-inter-clb-moi-gia-nhap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Matteo Politano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Inter Milan, CLB m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp. Anh hy v\u1ecdng s\u00e2n Giuseppe Meazza ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c mang l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Politano gia nh\u1eadp Inter</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Matteo Politano \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a Inter Milan trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng Radja Nainggolan, Stefan de Vrij v\u00e0 Roberto Gagliardini. Ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, Inter d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed9c c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Lazio \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a Serie A m\u00f9a 2017/18, Inter \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Champions League. C\u00e1c \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Trung Qu\u1ed1c quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 Nerazurri c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ee9c c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Politano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Inter Milan, CLB m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Politano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Inter Milan, CLB m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/politano-phat-bieu-ve-inter-clb-moi-gia-nhap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Politano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Inter sau khi gia nh\u1eadp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPolitano ch\u01a1i cho Sassuolo m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 10 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 4 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Inter theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 5 tri\u1ec7u Euro k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m sau.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nH\u00e1o h\u1ee9c ra s\u00e2n cho CLB m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft, Politano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Inter v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngay. \u201c<em>T\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t khi t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i</em>\u201d, m\u0169i c\u00f4ng 24 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Inter TV. \u201c<em>T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch, CLB, ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t</em>.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>T\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Sassuolo \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap t\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gia nh\u1eadp Inter. Giuseppe Meazza l\u00e0 s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 mang l\u1ea1i cho t\u00f4i may m\u1eafn. T\u00f4i t\u1eebng ghi b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea3 Inter v\u00e0 Milan t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ghi b\u00e0n cho trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Inter</em>.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Politano \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0110T Italia d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi t\u00e2n HLV Roberto Mancini. Anh c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 5 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Inter tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mu-chot-57-trieu-bang-cho-hau-ve-cua-inter-milan-421-188723.html\">MU ch\u1ed1t 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Inter Milan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/icardi-muon-o-lai-inter-milan-trong-tuong-lai-176-187519.html\">S\u1ebfp Inter b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Chelsea v\u00e0 Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/2-doi-bong-italia-muon-danh-bai-mu-vu-sao-tottenham-172-187269.html\">2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i MU v\u1ee5 sao Tottenham</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-muon-giai-cuu-bom-xit-cua-chelsea-172-186963.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u bom x\u1ecbt c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3918","checkdouble":"190095"},{"date":"13:55 01/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 19h00 ng\u00e0y 1/7 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/1/quang-ninh-vs-ha-noi-vong-17-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00f2ng 17 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 1/7.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC v\u00f2ng 17 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 1/7.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/quang-ninh-vs-ha-noi-vong-17-vleague-2018-372-190090.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP QU\u1ea2NG NINH VS H\u00c0 N\u1ed8I</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3917","checkdouble":"190090"},{"date":"13:52 01/07","title":"Petr Cech khi\u1ebfn t\u00e2n binh 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Arsenal c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y lo s\u1ee3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/petr-cech-khien-tan-binh-25-trieu-bang-cua-arsenal-cam-thay-lo-so.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Petr Cech ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno, c\u1ef1u sao Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Arsenal.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Bernd Leno</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/clb-arsenal-chinh-thuc-trinh-lang-tan-binh-thu-hai-trong-he-2018-172-188980.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Bernd Leno </span>t\u1eeb Bayer Leverkusen. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u, nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i h\u1ecd m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Petr Cech ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Petr Cech ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Petr-Cech-phat-bieu-ve-Bernd-Leno-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Bernd Leno</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n anh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Leno nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea9y Petr Cech ho\u1eb7c David Ospina ra \u0111i. Hi\u1ec7n Cech c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Ospina v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Petr Cech th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Leno</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Petr Cech ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno, c\u1ef1u sao Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Arsenal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cech thach thuc Leno cho vi tri so 1 trong khung go Arsenal\" title=\"Cech th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Leno cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/petr-cech-khien-tan-binh-25-trieu-bang-cua-arsenal-cam-thay-lo-so.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cech th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Leno cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb Napoli nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Leno\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Leno l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho Arsenal, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Cech t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi m\u1eddi c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ospina s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates. Hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 v\u00e0 Italia mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3916","checkdouble":"190087"},{"date":"14:42 01/07","title":"Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Arsenal c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/chot-thoi-diem-arsenal-cong-bo-tan-binh-25-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Torreira t\u1eeb Sampdoria, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Lucas Torreira</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRamsey ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2019 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Jack Wilshere ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. HLV Unai Emery bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/chot-thoi-diem-arsenal-cong-bo-tan-binh-25-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Lucas Torreira\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLucas Torreira c\u1ee7a Sampdoria l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Arsenal nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia. Ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n khi t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Torreira \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1edbi 36 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Serie A v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Anh l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Italia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Sampdoria x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1eafp b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Uruguay \u1edf World Cup 2018, anh c\u0169ng tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. R\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, Lucas Torreira khi\u1ebfn\u00a0Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/neville-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-arsenal-sau-tran-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-469-190073.html\" target=\"_blank\">Gary Neville khen Lucas Torreira</span>, c\u1ef1u sao M.U \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996, Gary Neville tin r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay t\u1edbi Emirates, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Arsenal s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal s\u1ebd c\u00f3 Torreira v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Torreira t\u1eeb Sampdoria, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal chieu mo Torreira voi gia 30 trieu euro\" title=\"Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/chu-tich-sampdoria-xac-nhan-ban-sao-khung-cho-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal s\u1ebd c\u00f3 Lucas Torreira v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u1edd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nUruguay s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 6 th\u00e1ng 7, Torreira l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3915","checkdouble":"190091"},{"date":"14:58 01/07","title":"Liverpool \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Karius","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/28/liverpool-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-karius.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Loris Karius g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Klopp ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Loris Karius</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLoris Karius l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c mang v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Simon Mignolet.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Loris Karius \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Loris Karius \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/Tuong-lai-Loris-Karius-duoc-HLV-Klopp-quyet-dinh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Klopp ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Karius</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh Karius \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt Mignolet \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c trong khung g\u1ed7. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1\u00a02018 v\u1edbi Real Madrid, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf 2/3 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a Liverpool, khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-3. Sau nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda n\u00e0y Karius g\u1eb7p \u00e1p l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool n\u00ean t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Liverpool s\u1ebd mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed The Kop c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, theo The Sun v\u00e0 ESPN, HLV Klopp s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong khung g\u1ed7 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, theo \u0111\u00f3 Karius ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a The Kop \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng theo ESPN, HLV Klopp s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf v\u00e0i ch\u1ee5c tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao nh\u01b0 Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma hay Courtois c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/liverpool-chap-nhan-that-bai-vu-thu-mon-79-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool kh\u00f4ng mua Alisson \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-liverpool-o-he-2018-172-181789.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m Jack Butland</span> c\u1ee7a Stoke City, song th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bet365.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Liverpool kh\u00f4ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Mignolet s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Anfield. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3914","checkdouble":"190092"}]}